%% DALP XVP (Exchange vs Payment) atomic settlement flow.
%% Shows DVP settlement: trade matching, compliance pre-check, atomic lock, simultaneous delivery, finality.
%% Use in settlement, DvP, post-trade, and counterparty risk sections.
%% Evaluator focus: counterparty risk elimination, atomic finality, failure rollback.
%%{init: {
  "theme": "base",
  "themeVariables": {"fontFamily": "Figtree, Inter, Arial, sans-serif", "fontSize": "15px", "textColor": "#1A1A2E", "lineColor": "#6B7280", "background": "#FFFFFF"},
  "sequence": {"mirrorActors": false, "showSequenceNumbers": false, "diagramMarginX": 40, "diagramMarginY": 20, "messageMargin": 28, "boxMargin": 12, "actorMargin": 40, "width": 170, "height": 64},
  "securityLevel": "loose"
}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant BUY as Buyer
    participant SELL as Seller
    participant API as Unified API
    participant XVP as XVP Engine
    participant CE as Compliance Engine
    participant ID as OnchainID
    participant BC as Blockchain<br/>(SMART Protocol)

    Note over BUY,BC: Trade Initiation and Matching

    BUY->>API: Submit buy order (asset, quantity, payment)
    SELL->>API: Submit sell order (asset, quantity, price)
    API->>XVP: Match trade (buyer + seller)
    XVP->>XVP: Validate trade terms

    Note over BUY,BC: Compliance Pre-Check (Both Parties)

    XVP->>CE: Pre-check buyer eligibility
    CE->>ID: Verify buyer OnchainID + claims
    ID-->>CE: Buyer identity valid
    CE-->>XVP: Buyer approved

    XVP->>CE: Pre-check seller eligibility
    CE->>ID: Verify seller OnchainID + claims
    ID-->>CE: Seller identity valid
    CE-->>XVP: Seller approved

    Note over BUY,BC: Atomic Settlement

    XVP->>BC: Lock buyer payment (escrow)
    BC-->>XVP: Payment locked
    XVP->>BC: Lock seller asset (escrow)
    BC-->>XVP: Asset locked

    alt Both locks successful
        XVP->>BC: Execute atomic swap (asset + payment)
        BC-->>XVP: Settlement finality confirmed
        XVP-->>API: Settlement complete
        API-->>BUY: Asset received
        API-->>SELL: Payment received
    else Lock failure or timeout
        XVP->>BC: Release buyer payment (rollback)
        XVP->>BC: Release seller asset (rollback)
        BC-->>XVP: Rollback confirmed
        XVP-->>API: Settlement failed
        API-->>BUY: Funds returned
        API-->>SELL: Asset returned
    end

    Note over XVP: [CLIENT: Configure settlement window, payment rail, and escrow policies here]
